<p><strong>What is this option?</strong><br>The position that your emojis appear above your button when your visitor engages with it.</p><p>Use this option when placing your button on the left or right side of your pages and posts. So, when your visitor hovers over your button, the emoji reactions will swing out in the opposite direction.</p><p><strong>Try this to see how it works by clicking on the preview tab to the right.</strong></p>